relation: Changed line numbering to have hybrid default.
Fixed a bug with the relative/absolute number switching in vim
Changed vim default shell to bash, because it just works better than fish in vim
Fixed a bug where the prompt would not display the branch if we are not at the root directory of a repository.
Temporaly left the option to change things at startup.
Changed the open from alias to function to allow multiple arguments.
Merged all pacnews. Added friendly interactive shell config files.
Added a history control to bash.
Set relative line numbering as default.
Changed the script according to Pylint reccomandations.
Added an option to scroll before the end of the viewable page to vim.
Fix a typo in ls options.
Enables modeline, removes auto nerdtree and enables wildmenu.
Changed to have a short list of packages without the description.
Added the list of the packages to the repository.
Use vim for editing of git config message and change default push strategy to 'matching'.
Added l33t plugin Conque for vim.
removed ARM toolchain from path as we dont build on ARM.
Added an alias to have human readable output from ls -l.
